data.title: Swiatek vs Paolini French Open Highlights: Swiatek beats Paolini, clinches title
data.meta_description: Iga Swiatek vs Jasmine Paolini French Open 2024 Highlights: Follow highlights of women's singles final, at Roland Garros on Saturday.
data.text:
Iga Swiatek vs Jasmine Paolini French Open 2024 Live Updates: Swiatek serves for the title, ad it is 15-0 for the Pole. 15-15.

Swiatek volleys it, 30-15. Swiatek sends it out, and it is 30-30. Swiatek makes it 40-30 and match point now! Paolini sends it out, SWIATEK WINS!

Swiatek 6-1 Paolini, second set

Iga Swiatek vs Jasmine Paolini French Open 2024 Live Updates: 30-0 for Swiatek and the Pole is in control now! Paolini serves and needs to fightback. She nets her first serve, serves again. Paolini fails to hit Swiatek's strong backhand well, goes out, 40-0 for the Pole. Swiatek takes the opening set!

Swiatek 6-2 Paolini, first set

Iga Swiatek vs Jasmine Paolini French Open 2024 Live Updates: Poor lob by Swiatek, goes out. 15-0 for Swiatek. The Italian serves, and nets it, serves again. A strong forehand sees her make it 15-15. Swiatek makes it 30-15. Swiatek sends it out, too much of power, 30-30. Swiatek makes it 40-30. Swiatek wraps this game.

Swiatek 4-2 Paolini, first set

Iga Swiatek vs Jasmine Paolini French Open 2024 Live Updates: Paolini is leading 40-0 in the second game. She serves, quick exchanges, and Swiatek is trying to dictate the game, and gets the point, 40-15.

GOOD HITTING! SWIATEK MAKES PAOLINI RUN HERE AND THEN SENDS IT TO THE OTHER SIDE, 40-30. OUT BY PAOLINI AND IT IS DEUCE NOW! GOOD VOLLEY BY SWIATEK, TAKES THE ADVANTAGE! OUT AND DEUCE AGAIN!

Swiatek sends it out, advantage to Paolini. Out by Swiatek again and Paolini gets the second game, good service hold!

Swiatek 1-1 Paolini

Iga Swiatek vs Jasmine Paolini French Open 2024 Live Updates: Swiatek wins the toss and opts to serve. The Pole serves, short exchanges and Paolini sends it out! 15-0! 30-0!

Paolini handles the bakchand and makes it 15-30. Good serve by Swiatek and Paolini nets the return, 40-15. Swiatek nets her return, 40-30! Swiatek wraps it up!

Swiatek 1-0 Paolini

Iga Swiatek vs Jasmine Paolini French Open 2024 Live Updates: Swiatek's French Open title defence alost ended in the opening week, as she faced a match point vs Osaka in the second round. But she fought back and cruised through her other games for a place in the final.

Iga Swiatek vs Jasmine Paolini French Open 2024 Live Updates: Swiatek leads 2-0 against Paolini in terms of head-to-head, and they first played against each other in Prague, six years ago, and it is their only match-up on clay. They next took on each other in the first round of Swiatek's title-winning run at the 2022 US Open.

Iga Swiatek vs Jasmine Paolini French Open 2024 Live Updates: Paolini will be in the top-10 for the first time in the upcoming WTA rankings. She is Italy's first woman to reach the final at Roland Garros since her current doubles partner Sara Errani came runners-up 12 years ago. It will be interesting to see if she joins 2010 champ Francesca Shiavone as the only Italian to have clinched the French Open title.
